    </reapack>
    <reapack name="Vintage Analog Synthesizer" type="effect" desc="Classic Analog-Style Synthesizer">
      <metadata>
        <description><![CDATA[
# TaalTools - Vintage Analog Synthesizer

A faithful recreation of classic analog synthesizer sounds with hardware-like characteristics.

## Features
- Two oscillators with classic waveforms (Saw, Square, Sine, Triangle, Noise)
- Analog-style drift and imperfections
- State variable filter (LP/BP/HP)
- Drive control for analog-style saturation
- True stereo output with subtle stereo width
]]></description>
      </metadata>
      <version name="1.1" author="Taal">
        <changelog><![CDATA[Initial Release]]></changelog>
        <source file="Effects/Vintage_Analog_Synth.jsfx">https://github.com/OseMine/TaalTools/raw/main/Effects/Vintage_Analog_Synth.jsfx</source>
      </version>
    </reapack>
    <reapack name="VA Synthesizer Extended" type="effect" desc="Extended Vintage-Style Synthesizer">
      <metadata>
        <description><![CDATA[
# TaalTools - VA Synthesizer Extended

An extended version of the vintage analog synthesizer with additional waveforms and features.

## Features
- Classic waveforms (Saw, Square, Sine, Triangle, Noise)
- Additional waveforms: Pulse (with variable width), SuperSaw, Hard Sync
- Analog-style saturation and warmth
- MIDI responsive with velocity
- Sub oscillator with adjustable mix
]]></description>
      </metadata>
      <version name="1.0" author="Taal">
        <changelog><![CDATA[Initial Release]]></changelog>
